702912f-b.text:
East 92nd Street, west side, between Avenues J and K, showing the Grace Methodist Episcopal Church. The view is east along the old road that led to the Lott House, the church being located at the S. W. corner of this road and East 92nd Stroet,
before the former was abandoned.
View 1: January, 1928
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
VViews 2,3
July e, 1933
P. L. Sperr
